Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.43,0:00:03.38,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:06.78,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:10.15,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since then, no matter \Nhow many times I call,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:11.20,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he doesn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:18.20,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think about it at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:22.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,but what kind of magic could connect
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:23.67,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,this room with the queen's?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:26.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even heard \Nof something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:30.03,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,A spell that connects you \Nto your desired location...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:32.28,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,We have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:40.87,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:42.44,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.38,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:51.39,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there hot water \Ncoming out of the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.39,0:00:53.23,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,This is the wrath of the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:55.46,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to die! I'm so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:57.97,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're overreacting. \NIt's just a hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.33,0:00:59.68,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.68,0:01:00.98,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,A natural phenomenon where
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:02.58,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,hot water springs from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.97,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,It is common to take \Nbaths in this water.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:07.78,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,T-Take baths?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:12.59,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:14.36,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the right temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:15.29,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:17.31,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,able to take a hot \Nspring bath over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:20.17,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good for your skin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.17,0:01:21.98,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,There was one back in my village, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.05,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:25.59,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Let's have a party here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:26.26,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,A party?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:27.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:28.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to invite Guiche
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.46,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,and the others once we \Nsettled down a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:32.80,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,but since we're all here, \Nlet's go for a dip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:36.35,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Get in it together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:38.39,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be fun. Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:13.97,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(720,1}Trouble at the Outdoor Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.41,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, please lend me your ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:18.51,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,The second in command of our
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.87,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Order of the Undine Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:23.27,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,and the new lord of \NDe Ornierés, Saito,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:27.02,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,has invited us to a grand opening party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:30.97,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, apparently
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.81,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,there's this thing called a\N"hot spring" on his land.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.21,CRZero,Reynald,0000,0000,0000,,That's something like a bath, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.18,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,According to Saito's letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.67,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,it's customary in a hot spring to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.00,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,interact in the nude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:46.14,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,In the nude... That means, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:52.65,CRZero,All,0000,0000,0000,,Long live the Order of \Nthe Undine Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.72,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that your skin gets so
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:57.07,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,unbelievably beautiful \Nafter a hot spring visit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:59.05,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,that you can make any man yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.32,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Then Jean will finally be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:05.18,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.13,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to the party, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:09.89,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:13.64,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be able to see Saito soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:28.59,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So there's only one tub?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.07,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get in \Nat different times.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.58,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,First the women go in, \Nthen the guys go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.24,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,This truly is any man's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:43.74,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.57,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You totally just pictured \Nthe other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:50.67,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:53.80,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Screw this hot spring. \NI'm not getting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.29,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's all for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It was my dream to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:05:00.08,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,get in a hot spring together \Nwith someone I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:01.95,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,T-Together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.50,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Get in with me, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.32,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be so embarrassed, I'd die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.78,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.26,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.35,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:23.78,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to thank \Nyou for before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.35,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.37,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.56,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to make up with Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.66,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Really, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:38.45,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,The next time something \Nhappens, I'm taking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.63,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's finally the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:51.88,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta, what are the \Nplans for tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.34,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Please rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.97,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to prepare \Na feast true to its name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.00,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:59.66,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't eaten anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.64,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.46,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:08.65,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, my sister eats like a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.30,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But since the hot spring is finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.28,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'd want her to get in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:18.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.68,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get up early tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:21.59,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.63,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,My foot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.20,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.84,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that, you have \Nto lay your egg quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:33.41,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get any more chances!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:36.26,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you in love with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.57,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:40.84,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:57.31,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize it got so late
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.75,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,while we were getting \Nready for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.56,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, Louise is already sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.48,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now we're alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.56,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.20,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've always wanted to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.75,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:25.83,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:28.91,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.75,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That voice was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:37.72,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tabitha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:41.04,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Please just keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:43.88,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But, you? Keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.67,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I want you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:47.90,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,to have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But, wait, Tabit—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:54.54,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, I know what I said earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:56.70,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll actually get \Nin the hot spring, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.81,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tabitha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:03.79,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:04.53,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:06.40,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Care to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:09.03,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think! \NI mistook her for you and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:10.26,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Mistook?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.60,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, just like you, her chest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.48,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What about her chest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.94,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.90,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,This is a what you call \Nan unfortunate accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.15,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,L-Louise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:26.18,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who's like me is out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:32.39,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm his master, \Nnaturally I'm by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:35.26,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm his maid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think this will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:42.23,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,How about we settle it \Nwith rock paper scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:44.62,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in charge of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.77,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Um... So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:47.74,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:51.21,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.70,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.29,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't sleep without Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.11,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,No sneaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.93,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:08.38,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:09.90,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.38,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:16.70,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.65,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:22.72,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:25.37,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:27.93,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Our guests have just arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.68,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.56,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche! Guys! Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:36.85,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,So Saito's finally a lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.77,CRZero,Reynald,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a move up the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.28,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it! \NThe nude interaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:44.23,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the hot spring feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:48.40,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,What? You haven't even kissed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.91,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha's not like you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:53.82,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,But if she goes back to Gallia \Nwithout having done anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.91,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,coming here was pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.41,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Congratulations, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:09:59.41,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.45,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.73,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What? Someone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.49,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:08.81,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:10.44,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That person is the \Ndefinition of suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.63,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up, you creeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.89,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.40,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty?!
