Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.48,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't want to lie to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:34.39,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,myself about my feelings any longer.
