Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.39,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that was good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:50.29,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But when I came here, I finally \Nunderstood what I'm here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:52.96,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
