Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.90,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, only look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.60,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.01,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.03,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:24.79,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was born for \Nthis moment, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:36.47,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why is Tiffa here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:42.60,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You promised, no cheating, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:44.90,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why she's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.48,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:49.12,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You should just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:54.24,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.89,0:23:30.60,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, the Elemental Siblings \Nare gunning for us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:33.46,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What? And elves are attacking, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:35.20,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Elves from the Desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:36.86,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.86,0:23:40.52,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you and Tiffa \Nalone at an oasis?!
